Description_lang: Imperator Mar'gok summons an Arcane mine under a random enemy that arms after 3 seconds. The mine persists for 1 minute and triggers if any player enters its radius after it arms.When triggered, Destructive Resonance explodes, inflicting $156673s1 Arcane damage to all players within its radius when triggered, increasing their Arcane damage taken by $159200s1% for $159200d.Replication: When Destructive Resonance detonates or expires, two additional Destructive Resonances are created nearby.
